parts.text:
<OUTPUT_JSON>
[
  {
    "selector": "input[name*=account i]",
    "description": "Account identifier input field. Used to enter the account code or name for recording a transaction.",
    "action_type": "type"
  },
  {
    "selector": "input[name*=amount i], input[type=number]",
    "description": "Transaction amount input field. Used to enter the monetary value for recording a transaction.",
    "action_type": "type"
  },
  {
    "selector": "textarea[name*=memo i]",
    "description": "Memo or description textarea. Used to add a note or detailed description for the transaction being recorded.",
    "action_type": "type"
  },
  {
    "selector": "button:has-text(\"post\" i), button:has-text(\"save\" i)",
    "description": "Action button to post or save the accounting entry. This action stores the recorded information.",
    "action_type": "click"
  }
]
</OUTPUT_JSON>
